{"tid":1015342,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"戴過帽真係好難再去相信人","createTime":"2019-02-10T01:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T15:51:19.000Z","uid":34921,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4807e7ecccee48b25277db1cba8c8458533f099f","tid":1015342,"uid":34921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T01:44:17.000Z","msg":"個陰影真係永遠都會留係到<br />\n年幾兩年前機緣巧合發現自己由頭綠到腳趾尾<br />\n詳細就唔講 免得相認<br />\n<br />\n過左咁耐 <br />\n有時到夜晚靜靜地訓唔著就會諗返當時既場面<br />\n再加上人大左<br />\n身邊都好多呢d事情出現<br />\n唔係呢個死黨比人綠<br />\n就係果個兄弟比人呃<br />\n而連登呢到都成日有綠帽post<br />\n由 睇連登狗公post見到自己條女果個post<br />\n到早兩日既阿可阿豆<br />\n<br />\n我越黎越覺得女人好恐怖<br />\n呢半年唔係無女仔埋身<br />\n但始終都係無勇氣再去相信一個人<br />\n<br />\n而家有個女仔約我情人節出街<br />\n我都唔知去唔去好"},{"pid":"b3e13fb4258df9c17c0caa126b1b349613d009eb","tid":1015342,"uid":109459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T01:50:08.000Z","msg":"其實呢個世界乜都會發生，應該信多Ｄ自己。。。"},{"pid":"8ef26eb5a742c4e539c67f6091e241207ae9fa0c","tid":1015342,"uid":198165,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T01:54:54.000Z","msg":"唔想收帽，兄弟你可以先派帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bff3cd824cabf0e471b9e236602142012c23ae","tid":1015342,"uid":181093,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCveYvy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCveYvy.png&h=b9b60eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e08bbff3c88ee1574c3e9fbd6ba72f7474ca441","tid":1015342,"uid":208364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:38:03.000Z","msg":"好驚再拍拖，最後又係得返自己孤零零一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ea60b9ed469a5093b787c69eda335f6b495f99","tid":1015342,"uid":9467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"岩岩發現自己帶左帽 搵緊機會攤牌"},{"pid":"7591782d5adf1f55a913198b137d619604940c84","tid":1015342,"uid":34921,"lik